snippet.title: Cricket Through the Ages | Swinging for PC and Switch on March 1
snippet.description:
Developed by Free Lives (Terra Nil, Broforce, Gorn), mobile smash hit Cricket Through the Ages is now making its way to PC and Nintendo Switch!

Enjoy cricket through the miracle of a simple, one-button control scheme
Play through six unique game modes, solo or against a friendly rival
Learn about the totally real history of cricket. You won’t believe it!

Go alone, or take a friend, on a journey through the rich and 100% accurate history of the sport in Cricket Through the Ages, launching on PC and Nintendo Switch on March 1.
